# IEEE CASS Kerala Chapter Website

This project is a responsive website prototype for the IEEE Circuits and Systems Society (CASS) Kerala Chapter.
This website prototype was built using Next.js and Tailwind CSS. 
v0.dev was used as an AI-assisted prototyping tool to generate the initial UI structure, 
after which the design and components were customized manually. 
Version control was managed using Git and GitHub, and the site was deployed using Vercel.

## Features
- Hero landing section introducing IEEE CASS
- About section explaining the society and chapter mission
- Events section displaying upcoming and past events
- Team section showing executive committee members
- Contact section with form and social media icons
- Fully responsive design for mobile and desktop

## Tools and Frameworks Used
- Next.js (React framework)
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- TypeScript
- Git and GitHub for version control
- Deployment using Vercel
-v0.dev (AI-assisted UI prototyping)

## Live Website
https://ieee-kerala-cass.vercel.app

